---
description: UI-only component rules
globs: src/**/*.component.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---

Components render prepared props only.

Forbidden here: hooks, services, gateways, stores, queries, native APIs, browser APIs, raw user
copy, raw routes, raw endpoints, raw test ids, and module-scope supporting declarations.
Extract types to `*.types.ts`, constants to `*.constants.ts`, variants to `*.variants.ts`.
